
Attached is a link to Miller & Chevalier's December 2000 HIPAA Alert
regarding the final privacy rule.  This document is in pdf format and should
be viewed with Adobe Reader.
http://www.millerchevalier.com/public_library/HIPAAAlert122000.pdf

The August issue that is referenced in the December Alert is located at:
http://www.millerchevalier.com/public_library/HIPAAAlert82000.pdf

If you do not have Adobe Reader loaded on your computer, you may download it
from the Internet at no charge.  Simply click on this link to the Adobe web
site (http://www.adobe.com/prodindex/acrobat/readstep.html) and follow the
simple instructions at the bottom of the page.

If you have difficulty opening the document, prefer to receive a copy by
mail, or if you would like to add a colleague's name to the distribution
list, contact Ashley Vance (E-mail: avance@milchev.com or Telephone: (202)
626-5885).

